{"tid":946482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓旅館發現三名高中生死亡　另有七人昏迷","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T15:06:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d3cc542acbbad0980ed6865634ec8c303d7420","tid":946482,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:18:44.000Z","msg":"南韓消防人員在江陵市一間旅館，發現十名青少年，其中三人當場死亡，七人昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述警方表示，旅館內一氧化碳濃度很高，青少年被發現時口吐白沫，而且有嘔吐症狀，但初步斷定不涉自殺。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有報道指，他們是首爾一間高中的學生，考試後相約到當地遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n當局正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433907-20181218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433907-20181218.htm&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c51c4762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433907-20181218.htm&h=641de54b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433907-20181218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a4191168eba972798a359746537512f973a191e","tid":946482,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca94d9dc25822f814567057952a14931e57aa221","tid":946482,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"祭品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26600bac7f9213e751794c747ba08431435928f","tid":946482,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d813f44960c92332e09d9693a00f7d79a4ea25d","tid":946482,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"世越號"},{"pid":"5f0b3f84d8b062e316267174ce6a41b272b9b516","tid":946482,"uid":20241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:29:21.000Z